{
  "stem": "895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was in the time when Paul Whiteman started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was looking at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we grew up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I played some soccer, in London, as a boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to school there up till my 16th year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And during the war, in 1914, I can never forget-- I was standing on the balcony-- I saw the zeppelins coming over, that time, being shot down, on fire-- see the Germans falling out.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was seven years old that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That memory, I remember very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, after that, 1914-- 1918, the war stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was 18.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember in between, after the war stopped, we went back to Holland for my bar mitzvah to be celebrated in the Spanish and Portuguese synagogue in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For a holiday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All the family were living in England with us, that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we went back to England again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a few years, my father said he wants to go and live in Holland again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a-- I was a member of the Spanish and Portuguese synagogue in London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bevis Marks-- that was the name, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The synagogue was just built like the one in Amsterdam, but smaller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was in the choir there-- in the choir of the Spanish and Port-- and then, I remember-- I don't wear it now, but I got a tzitzit and everything, because-- And then, after that, we enjoyed our-- member of the North London Jewish Club in London, where we had plays and sports and everything.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I made a good friend there-- Shapiro was his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stuck together always, till the time my father said, I want to go back to Holland and start a factory of my own.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
